---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="DMCA Policy — mp4yt"
  description="DMCA takedown policy for mp4yt.com. Learn how to submit a DMCA notice if you believe your copyrighted content is being accessed through our service."
  canonicalUrl="https://mp4yt.com/dmca"
>
  <Navbar />
  <main id="main-content">
    <section class="legal-hero">
      <div class="page-container">
        <span class="eyebrow">Legal</span>
        <h1 class="display-xl legal-title">DMCA Policy</h1>
        <p class="body-lg legal-subtitle">Digital Millennium Copyright Act Notice</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="legal-body">
      <div class="page-container legal-container">
        <div class="legal-content">

          <h2 class="display-sm">Our Commitment</h2>
          <p>
            mp4yt respects the intellectual property rights of content creators and copyright holders.
            We comply with the Digital Millennium Copyright Act (DMCA) and will respond promptly to
            valid takedown notices.
          </p>

          <hr class="legal-divider" />

          <h2 class="display-sm">Important Context</h2>
          <p>
            mp4yt does <strong>not</strong> host, store, or redistribute any video content. Our service
            extracts metadata (title, thumbnail, duration) and provides the direct CDN stream URL
            from the original hosting platform. The actual video content is served directly from the
            platform's own content delivery network (e.g., YouTube's, Instagram's, TikTok's CDN).
          </p>
          <p>
            If your content is hosted on a platform like YouTube or Instagram, the most effective
            approach is to submit a DMCA notice directly to that platform, which has the ability
            to remove the content at its source.
          </p>

          <hr class="legal-divider" />

          <h2 class="display-sm">Filing a DMCA Takedown Notice</h2>
          <p>
            If you believe your copyrighted work is being accessed through our Service in a way
            that constitutes copyright infringement, please send a DMCA takedown notice to our
            designated agent with the following information:
          </p>
          <ol>
            <li>
              <strong>Identification of the copyrighted work:</strong> Describe the copyrighted
              work you claim has been infringed.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Identification of the infringing material:</strong> Provide the specific URL(s)
              on mp4yt.com that you believe are infringing, or the original video URL being accessed.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Your contact information:</strong> Include your full name, mailing address,
              telephone number, and email address.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Good faith statement:</strong> A statement that you have a good faith belief
              that use of the material is not authorized by the copyright owner, its agent, or the law.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Accuracy statement:</strong> A statement, under penalty of perjury, that the
              information in your notice is accurate and that you are the copyright owner or authorized
              to act on the owner's behalf.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Signature:</strong> Your physical or electronic signature.
            </li>
          </ol>

          <hr class="legal-divider" />

          <h2 class="display-sm">Where to Send Notices</h2>
          <div class="contact-card">
            <p><strong>DMCA Agent</strong></p>
            <p>
              Email: <a href="mailto:dmca@mp4yt.com">dmca@mp4yt.com</a><br/>
              Subject line: <code>DMCA Takedown Notice</code>
            </p>
          </div>
          <p>
            We will respond to valid DMCA notices within 48 hours. Please note that we may forward
            your notice to the user who submitted the URL for extraction.
          </p>

          <hr class="legal-divider" />

          <h2 class="display-sm">Counter-Notification</h2>
          <p>
            If you believe your content was wrongly taken down, you may submit a counter-notification
            to our DMCA Agent. The counter-notification must include:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>Your physical or electronic signature</li>
            <li>Identification of the material that was removed</li>
            <li>A statement under penalty of perjury that the material was removed by mistake</li>
            <li>Your name, address, and telephone number</li>
            <li>Consent to jurisdiction of the federal court in your district</li>
          </ul>

          <hr class="legal-divider" />

          <h2 class="display-sm">Repeat Infringers</h2>
          <p>
            In appropriate circumstances, we will terminate access for users who are repeat
            infringers. Since we don't require user accounts, this is implemented through
            rate-limiting and URL-level blocking.
          </p>

        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .legal-hero {
    background-color: var(--color-canvas);
    padding: var(--sp-5xl) var(--sp-lg) var(--sp-3xl);
    text-align: center;
  }
  .legal-title {
    margin: var(--sp-sm) 0 0;
    color: var(--color-ink);
  }
  .legal-subtitle {
    margin: var(--sp-xs) 0 0;
    color: var(--color-mute);
  }
  .legal-body {
    background-color: var(--color-canvas-soft);
    padding: var(--sp-4xl) var(--sp-lg);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-hairline);
  }
  .legal-container {
    max-width: 720px;
  }
  .legal-content {
    background-color: var(--color-canvas);
    border-radius: var(--rounded-lg);
    padding: var(--sp-xl) var(--sp-xl);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-3);
  }
  .legal-content h2 {
    margin: var(--sp-xl) 0 var(--sp-md);
    color: var(--color-ink);
  }
  .legal-content h2:first-child {
    margin-top: 0;
  }
  .legal-content p,
  .legal-content li {
    color: var(--color-body);
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin: 0 0 var(--sp-sm);
  }
  .legal-content ul,
  .legal-content ol {
    padding-left: var(--sp-lg);
    margin: 0 0 var(--sp-md);
  }
  .legal-content li {
    margin-bottom: var(--sp-xs);
  }
  .legal-content a {
    color: var(--color-link);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.15s ease;
  }
  .legal-content a:hover {
    color: var(--color-link-deep);
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
  .legal-content code {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 13px;
    background-color: var(--color-canvas-soft-2);
    padding: 1px 5px;
    border-radius: 3px;
    color: var(--color-body);
  }
  .contact-card {
    background-color: var(--color-canvas-soft);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-hairline);
    border-radius: var(--rounded-md);
    padding: var(--sp-md) var(--sp-lg);
    margin: var(--sp-md) 0;
  }
  .contact-card p {
    margin: 0 0 var(--sp-xs);
  }
  .contact-card p:last-child {
    margin: 0;
  }
  .legal-divider {
    border: none;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-hairline);
    margin: var(--sp-xl) 0;
  }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .legal-hero { padding: var(--sp-4xl) var(--sp-md) var(--sp-xl); }
    .legal-content { padding: var(--sp-lg); }
  }
</style>
